      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. While the engine and transmission are solid, the exterior shows clear signs of use, including some minor paint chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining from age. It\u2019s a great car for someone who values mechanical reliability over a showroom finish.",
