    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, museum-grade example that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing zero signs of road wear or environmental exposure. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV damage or rattling. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with the precise tactile feel of a brand-new car. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified specialists using OEM parts. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage remains remarkably pristine. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-quality specimen for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
